  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-24cfa1e3-eb4e-4153-84f8-9e9d5bfa0d5e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d9b906f-1d64-41a8-bd20-2bd18c6e09d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81338ab1-9836-4a76-b22f-409d80f6b0cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>명함의 정의</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1492a7c0-8995-4878-98bf-fd261f0c6af5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-fd18ba18-fb47-4c8a-9885-003f5df375ed\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dc82aeab-a656-448b-b14b-8f36b435217d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">인쇄의 기본 명함에 대해 알아봅니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-3f731e04-8e1b-4935-b9d3-0613476ae55e\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-41816b6b-0b3d-436b-9622-e34ac3b24bad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfaf5325-751d-4c83-af3b-b487eb7ad0ea\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-28a88d9b-acf3-4436-865e-dea42466a554\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/alikeMeaning.naver?query=00144175\" target=\"_blank\"><b>명함</b></a></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2299d326-9ead-4660-b419-f49a09e4caf4\" style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>성명 ·주소 ·직업 등을 적은 소형 종이</b></span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-42e9f1f4-33ca-4534-8c90-28e54df301f3\" style=\"line-height:1.2;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b50c894c-7fc9-4519-9809-042b52900659\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1093302&amp;cid=40942&amp;categoryId=31611\" target=\"_blank\"><b>명함 [名啣]</b></a></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-030805a2-f769-4a85-b90b-d6fbaff7e6ba\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-78f4ca13-b285-4cc1-b6be-c18c5bfdeec3\" style=\"color:#559bfa;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/list.naver?cid=40942&amp;categoryId=40942\" target=\"_blank\">두산백과 두피디아</a></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f49a15e-a06e-48ac-a934-1c3c2412c295\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-75a6be27-fa99-4083-b6a5-7931da71fc24\" style=\"color:#303030;background-color:#ffffff;\">성명 ·주소 ·직업 등을 적은 소형 종이. 옛날 중국에서 대나무를 깎아 이름을 적은 데서 비롯되었다고 한다. 오늘날에는 인쇄한 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-579cc763-08c3-4c3a-8836-ec7f514481f6\" style=\"color:#303030;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>명함</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cf0eb079-3c09-4d76-8aef-2d605548066e\" style=\"color:#303030;background-color:#ffffff;\">을 사용하는 것이 보통이고, 외국에서는 주로 이름만 적는데, 한국에서는 이름 외에 주소 ·전화번호 ·직장 ·직위 등을 기입한다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5fa5bea7-f43f-45a1-a0d4-5aa2f715d8a4\" style=\"color:#303030;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>명함</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0cdb8f2d-eb14-400e-b415-a06fb30535c9\" style=\"color:#303030;background-color:#ffffff;\">의 모양 ·크기도 나라마다 여러 가지인데, 현재 한국에서 사용하고 있는 것이 일반적이며, 영국 ·미국에서는 여성용...</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-949b1762-c1f7-4c30-b749-3050b8b7730e\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f64f910c-3f77-4b06-9e6a-98d1fbad89ac\" style=\"color:#888888;background-color:#ffffff;\">관련정보</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ab38826b-bef3-404e-971d-8180265279d4\" style=\"color:#0033ac;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1058517&amp;ref=y\" target=\"_blank\">거향잡의</a></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-560c7886-ff9c-458c-a4fe-0747f57ab81f\" style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\">, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b00a726c-5538-4489-887b-253104d78c69\" style=\"color:#0033ac;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1113371&amp;ref=y\" target=\"_blank\"><u>세함</u></a></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ed04c70a-1f28-43e7-b4b4-2bfb20464320\" style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\">, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ab27e626-0c7d-4c5b-9b18-50076e83aea3\" style=\"color:#0033ac;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1149889&amp;ref=y\" target=\"_blank\">켄트지</a></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f999c191-def7-406c-bcc6-7859e3255040\" style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\">, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3b6b79f4-c968-4277-b231-5b065216ebe0\" style=\"color:#0033ac;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1152038&amp;ref=y\" target=\"_blank\">타이포그래피</a></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-97e730cc-de32-41c4-99ee-6e849c9f2535\" style=\"color:#666666;background-color:#ffffff;\">, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-11df2742-f687-4211-a90c-39e97d23714b\" style=\"color:#0033ac;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1180053&amp;ref=y\" target=\"_blank\">로터스 노츠</a></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-acda4439-7011-4b51-ad6c-aba36b104d34\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e5c9fb31-52e6-4c67-bcee-37b0d9c96d9b\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a7d3c4d4-7cf6-47e4-a2be-bfcf06cab043\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-155ceb40-a448-46ae-9223-c5d8ab9ed337\" style=\"color:#0033ac;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a3cd893a-0c70-4557-a436-e966d722118b\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-24d660d8-8eaf-4a0c-9f32-fb528699dcf2\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">명함은 자신의 사업정보를 일반적인 규격에 담아 타인에게 전달하는 도구로 사용되는 인쇄물입니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5501b403-bb4f-443f-943d-9ce6586fc907\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4101cf54-cdd8-4306-87c0-5327254d1df5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c123d0b0-6ea0-4151-b363-c8aba829234d\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-63ee39c1-8ac3-457b-9af1-ff230c57eda8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">우리나라에서 IMF이후에 합판시장(Gain Print)이 태동했으며 직장을 잃은 이른바 가방쟁이(명함딜러)분들이 명함영업을 시작으로 저렴하게 인쇄하는 시장이 시작되었습니다. 그 무렵에 여러 합판업체가 생겨났으며 본인도 그 합판시장에 합류하여 사업을 했었습니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9be92a0b-6668-4f85-b7f0-b55ab6ca2b39\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ce899496-037a-489b-9c2e-8e5fb3d831cc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-96ba2ebd-0ea7-47cb-924d-cab76a6b07bb\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-46773537-2fb4-42a7-8cc6-7f4edc0140e4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">가장 일반적인 명함의 종류부터 설명을 시작합니다.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aa87870e-59b1-4cb8-ba11-84a2b7f8de31\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cee179c5-11bd-49cf-aaf0-798a10dbb3d1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-ff8b0900-a968-4656-86e2-3b9183b3ec22\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6b27b812-811f-4c41-8664-ef36e2244011\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a485eef9-ee81-4787-a02b-ba09143a1e71\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b5d8ee2b-53c9-4d46-b02b-ca86ac922299\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>일반명함 (코팅/무코팅명함)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5de6c803-5e95-44c8-97fc-c061de4aa580\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ecbdee08-4664-45fb-a432-50569df343ed\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aae091c2-c6fc-4013-996d-d5f7cababb18\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8876fbe2-5d7b-4806-95c0-890de5ad2461\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이설명에서 말씀드렸듯이 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b22be116-fe28-4a70-bcd4-60d9f43af049\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222894240385\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/222894240385</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3f72eb98-bc2f-43cb-8c54-e13bedd907fc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50e5a1e3-7fab-4250-8bdf-b8b72d732e77\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-00e749be-8534-475a-8164-7095a8458d37\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">우리나라 종이 소비의 엄청난 비율을 차지하는 아트/스노우지를 저렴(?)하게 구입하여 여러명의 오더를 모아서 인쇄하여 출력하므로서 가장 저렴하게 명함을 빠르게 공급하는 시장이 생겨났습니다. 이 일반명함은 요 근래에 막뿌리는 명함 즉, 흔히 말해 막 나눠주는 대량 명함시장으로 자리를 잡게 됩니다. 이유는 가격대비 효률이 높기 때문입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-336a27a2-8a36-4365-8b17-5b5679e38784\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2c6d7ec1-d4c8-4d17-a0e0-6d4dabcef925\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-17b2fed2-8b1d-42e6-9604-a6e06d2cd3fa\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a0cf6d69-8d51-4b7e-b504-03f98ce1558f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 디자인비 + 인쇄비포함 500장 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c99f6c1d-f389-4836-a842-868b52916ee2\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>15,000원</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-6f60c253-a0d8-454b-98a2-d469c5684fd6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(디자인, 로고 제공, 후공정, 지질 및 납기 등에 따라 변경될 수 있습니다.)에 공급하고 있습니다. 자세한 사항은 전화 또는 댓글로 부탁드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a83a7c8-a188-47c3-a6b4-003ef7ae8a3e\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f8d719d9-c1c6-4fa2-8bac-67da7ed89eed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-042f08ee-ade3-4f29-92e3-1bad7bf9ed56\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-565c77bf-3e57-4229-880f-daab33d2c354\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주요 사용처 : 부동산 명함, 커피숍 도장쿠폰, 보험회사 홍보용 명함, 기타 대량 소비용 업종</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da4e29bf-b9c9-49e1-abc7-948f2cc9faa1\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1aadf4d6-43c6-4de7-af69-3451d5bca39e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-65512ff5-e096-4e03-a00a-88b2bb055d6b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-16373f93-280d-447d-9407-c500ef50d743\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-baae1884-865f-4678-9010-95b946e01d2d\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bf616aa8-5463-4fbb-9a75-70cafacc44ad\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>고급명함 (수입지/카드명함)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a37f3e13-1360-4a72-bfbc-e39e07c875aa\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a577bfc8-9a62-43cb-b293-d0658a7a99fd\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-52ae1070-9b8b-471d-a388-0b4a33e5582d\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2fde0433-97b2-47c6-9676-64ee00ccc4f1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">합판 명함시장의 초창기에는 주문의 90%는 일반명함이었습니다. 그러나 몇년 후 시장이 커지고 고객의 요구가 다양해짐에 따라 종이의 특별함을 요구했고 몇몇업체가 uv인쇄의 시설투자와 함께 다양한 종의 인쇄를 시작하기에 이릅니다. 이는 휘라레(린넨커버), 반누브 등의 다양한 명함재질의 공급과 초창기 뒷면에 뒷묻음을 방지하기 위해 간지를 삽입해서 납품이 이루어지다가 차츰 하이브리드 uv인쇄방식을 채용하여 더 빠르게 더 낮은 가격으로 생산이 이루어 지게됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b5d54f5-a236-4151-a5c4-7f01a121011c\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2b2d932a-36fa-4211-9b34-426692f70a24\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b6059b0-6a40-49b0-baef-fe68169a6b5f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:233px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222897746493/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-93deb88c-0a26-434e-a0eb-8106193b0d58\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e9490207-13d8-40b5-976e-1c58ef2313c3\" style=\"\">고급명함의 종류</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42cc9984-a241-49bd-a48d-a2ee2e412376\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b05996c-b197-4d9a-b882-c642559131e0\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a33678c8-b683-450f-8644-63b539f7043a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-324fc9d4-0cf5-4899-8e9e-3e513d7ea6e2\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e5d1b0cc-bea9-49cb-a757-5a51e034d5ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-886de234-4eab-44fc-a2b9-5ec1341f972b\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-55520cf8-099e-4bce-b8c8-49e4a5951e9d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">카드명함은 Pet재질의 명함으로 규격이나 종류는 정해져 있습니다. 일반적으로 화이트 카드명함을 주로 사용하며 특별하게 찢어지지 않기 때문에 영구보관을 원하는 특별한 분들에게 적합합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bda937ab-dfe6-4e28-97d0-ee107b43ac3f\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-05186f74-9b89-4d5e-bfb3-cd680d2fd36f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bf8a13be-917c-4652-9caf-f0aa102918f2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:233px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222897746493/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6923910e-8820-4818-95fa-0bff0a24bbca\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7c9ad54c-57b9-4590-92f1-eeab6fb0187c\" style=\"\">카드명함의 종류</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eda57d53-d7d4-4986-9efc-144808afc65a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83d23383-c5d1-4fcd-a6ef-7f088a242b22\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-62c55907-8f2a-4f66-ae3a-05b6dfd9f1a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a16ee6ea-93dc-451c-87e6-4d38626b7ad7\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8489cf70-59c5-4a5d-b182-917a09c29b47\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 디자인비 + 인쇄비포함 200장 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5ef2e165-b070-4c81-9a42-81ba875eaf9f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>18,000원</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a7540850-8450-4e9e-b09a-7dce469807f5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(디자인, 로고 제공, 후공정, 지질 및 납기 등에 따라 변경될 수 있습니다.)에 공급하고 있습니다. 자세한 사항은 전화 또는 댓글로 부탁드립니다. 카드명함은 별도문의.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d06a6b19-49b0-4e20-86c9-d6005ea9bc0f\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0a7c1c41-c948-48be-a992-4d4d3c401ff0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f2efab9f-6e0a-4619-b837-b76496f2ec99\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-322330bb-2808-45d0-8b27-b253b0504b53\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주요 사용처 : 기업명함, 전문직등 개인명함 외 대부분의 명함</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0cc139c9-dbf8-43bb-88bd-5fa6b06e33f5\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f41fd400-1d89-4c5d-af76-2dd1a899e04f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-d2d45094-f38b-4769-bedc-75f6275e11e6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3edd512d-6a07-46d1-b18a-d783d21dc2a5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9b67768b-5350-4797-a8c6-799034ee365e\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e51fe09b-025e-464d-a61b-451fbd9aea56\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디지털명함 (다양한, 그리고 빠른명함)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5147f945-89a3-47e1-afe2-7f80423a649c\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f91bffe2-4ba1-4632-98cc-3b8b5ce6f849\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-32e416cd-8786-4530-9754-b95954e72179\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-93483f4d-6c42-4ab2-8e63-db9ed6f6f2de\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">10여년전부터 인쇄기기 시장에 디지털인쇄의 등장이 센세이션하게 다가왔습니다. 기본 옵셋(off-set)인쇄는 물과 잉크(기름)이 섞이지 않는 원리로 판막을 형성해서 인쇄하는 방식이었다면 요즘의 명함 시장은 디지털인쇄가 잠식해 가고 있는 중입니다. 디지털인쇄는 옵셋에 비해 처음장과 마지막장의 색이 거의 동일하게 골고루 출력이 되고 뒷묻음도 적고 그 무엇보다 빠르게 생산을 하는 장점을 가지고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-325e6ab4-50db-404f-8026-d6f91024287f\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0a571887-5ea8-4437-92b5-7570405a6cdb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b62a1af2-4716-4c66-8f1f-050a8623ddf4\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fb8db8cd-babf-483d-89c8-b6988adc084d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">대표적인 디지털 기기로는 인디고프레스, 아이젠 시리즈, 넥스프레스 등이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ecadd8d8-10d6-4215-892c-1a8422e63b41\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-075c5ce2-f546-410f-9837-9d82c56f800c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f48ab0db-647f-499c-a74f-f986533e4629\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9a0f6e46-9195-4f66-b611-d84138dacf10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-7cbce054-7bc1-45db-b501-ac6de773a683\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-384af0f4-310e-4544-9ca4-8684f09763f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-764ce301-d8df-4f20-b2a5-7990ad553165\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a37444cc-169b-4230-97fa-b81a68e04020\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>명함 주문시 주의 점</b></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-455e8a5c-2cd2-4d58-ba85-6553269fe272\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d5543f1d-d7d5-48e5-896b-1dba81967299\" style=\"color:#000000;\"><b>​</b></span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-136e3138-9599-4da4-a1b8-aaa6f3da2b2a\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-109b6abe-3d69-4c92-9f17-b084c0006dc4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> 로고 전송</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9bb4dd6-cfae-46b7-b1c2-d04a257d68d4\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-08fda74b-2c79-4e2c-9d7d-13405a9aa3b9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">자신의 기존 샘플 사진 제공</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07e33c2a-1f72-443d-b72b-8e50c0851353\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b850150e-76cb-42a8-b48f-66a1d0be1e54\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">명함에 들어가는 내용 정보 제공</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-67aa2332-22ac-4a78-b347-d34783cdb32c\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-592e9758-18db-44ef-9542-fa6c2bee7142\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">종이, 후공정, 인쇄방식, 납기 등 주의 점 전달</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08c2e0ae-973f-43fc-bee3-74eb0ae2a025\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3af59a73-17c3-4aa5-9935-ccace4926faa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-77423ce5-c8c5-4e3a-b965-5747f7f46d42\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9218a39e-09bc-4c79-85b7-bb69ac2a55f7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bd832f5a-d09c-4cb9-a671-0630de61cd96\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:828px;\">\n<div cla